latestIgtvVideos.title: GANAPATI KAUTHUVAM following thanjavur tradition of bharatanatyam.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Meaning : Divine nephew of vishnu (ari/hari)! Destroyer (vinayaka) of obstacles (vighna)!
Salutations (jaya jaya) to ganesha who blessed us by coming into being (aruliya) so that the consequences of our deeds (vinai) may perish.
One with a stout body (dadikkai), a trunk (tudikkai) and an elephant (yanai) face (mukhattavar)!
The one who leads (pati) the god's army of bhuta ganas!
Let the consequences of the deeds (vinai) of those that have learnt (katravar) this poem (kauttuvam) on ganesha be destroyed!

Video: @abhi_is_hekkk
